short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A powerful search bar that can run calculations, search your tabs and history, open new tabs, and more.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Boost your productivity with a Spotlight-like search bar for your web browser. Ctrl/Cmd+Shift+U opens it by default. You can search your tabs, bookmarks, and history, as well as use "del" to delete tabs, "search" to search the web, "open" to open a link, "calc" as a calculator (note - at the time of this writing, calc can only compute basic operations on 2 numbers; more may yield inaccurate results), "clear" to offer to clear your clipboard, "gen" to generate a password, and "new" to open a new tab/window/private window. Cybersearch is all you need to supercharge your workflow with an efficient terminal for your browser. Finally, a way to manage your entire browser from your keyboard.
Created by Revaant Srivastav
